c88d90daf8727a6c2f7f51ae23d\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke stands on a dock while wearing fancy armor. Ships set sail behind him.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen I first discovered the ornament vendor in \u003cem\u003eAssassin’s Creed Shadows\u003c/em\u003e—the kindly woman selling decorations and \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-hideout-customization-unlock-1851772163\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-hideout-customization-unlock-1851772163\"\u003ecustomization options for the hideout\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e—I had a feeling I’d end up spending tons of Mon decking out my dojo. Well, that assumption was correct. Many thousands of Mon later, I was rolling in rocks, trees, and roofing materials. But I was out of money. So I had to find some new strats to keep the cash flowing. - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-mon-treasure-valuables-settsu-1851772640\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-mon-treasure-valuables-settsu-1851772640\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7\" data-recommend-id=\"image://866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image of a character in a robe holding a staff while kneeling on their knees in a dark tunnel.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image of a character in a robe holding a staff while kneeling on their knees in a dark tunnel.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image of a character in a robe holding a staff while kneeling on their knees in a dark tunnel.\" data-chomp-id=\"866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"An image of a character in a robe holding a staff while kneeling on their knees in a dark tunnel.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: SenseGames\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7\" data-recommend-id=\"image://866c7eb80e2dcd0c6a70aa5d125f28e7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image of a character in a robe holding a staff while kneeling on their knees in a dark tunnel.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere is an abundance of soulslike titles these days, giving fans of the brutal genre plenty of options for where to spend their time exploring, making builds, and taking down extremely challenging bosses. If you’re an anime enthusiast as well, you may have had your eye on \u003cem\u003eAI Limit\u003c/em\u003e, which costs only $35. This may leave you wondering how long of a journey the game offers and whether it’s worth investing in. So let’s get into it. - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/ai-limit-soulslike-how-long-to-beat-short-hard-1851772663\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/ai-limit-soulslike-how-long-to-beat-short-hard-1851772663\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df\" data-recommend-id=\"image://787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Promotional art for Atomfall shows a person with an assault rifle looking out over a storm.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Promotional art for Atomfall shows a person with an assault rifle looking out over a storm.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Promotional art for Atomfall shows a person with an assault rifle looking out over a storm.\" data-chomp-id=\"787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Promotional art for Atomfall shows a person with an assault rifle looking out over a storm.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Rebellion\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df\" data-recommend-id=\"image://787c2d7c9c9dc569201c48426890b5df\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Promotional art for Atomfall shows a person with an assault rifle looking out over a storm.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo level your skills up in \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://cdkeys.pxf.io/c/379647/1566025/18216?subId1=KT\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdkeys.com%2Fatomfall-pc-steam\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://cdkeys.pxf.io/c/379647/1566025/18216?subId1=KT\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdkeys.com%2Fatomfall-pc-steam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eAtomfall\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, you’ll need to find Training Stimulants. And while you’ll have a solid selection of skills you can buy early on, you can add additional skills to your repertoire by finding manuals out in the world. But which to choose first?  - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/atomfall-skills-training-stimulant-fortitude-weapon-thr-1851772475\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/atomfall-skills-training-stimulant-fortitude-weapon-thr-1851772475\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A man walks toward the camera while wielding an assault rifle.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A man walks toward the camera while wielding an assault rifle.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A man walks toward the camera while wielding an assault rifle.\" data-chomp-id=\"44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"A man walks toward the camera while wielding an assault rifle.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Rebellion\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://44fb6822de2e0cd9ff1708e433eb743e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A man walks toward the camera while wielding an assault rifle.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere have been quite a few games over the years that examine the fallout of a nuclear event, but developer Rebellion’s new title \u003cem\u003eAtomfall\u003c/em\u003e distinguishes itself by using a real-life accident as the basis for its tale. Taking place in an alternate reality following the Windscale nuclear disaster of 1957, this UK-based survival-action experience provides a large open-world experience with plenty to do and see in a radioactive England. Here’s how long it’ll take you to see what \u003cem\u003eAtomfall\u003c/em\u003e has to offer. - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/atomfall-how-long-to-beat-finish-trophy-achievement-1851772231\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/atomfall-how-long-to-beat-finish-trophy-achievement-1851772231\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke standing before the main hideout entrance in Assassin’s Creed Shadows.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke standing before the main hideout entrance in Assassin’s Creed Shadows.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Yasuke standing before the main hideout entrance in Assassin’s Creed Shadows.\" data-chomp-id=\"1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Yasuke standing before the main hideout entrance in Assassin’s Creed Shadows.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Ubisoft / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1371d44a3a870da3ea7fd496daa62bc1\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke standing before the main hideout entrance in Assassin’s Creed Shadows.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eCustomization is one of my favorite parts of just about any video game, followed closely by base-building elements. \u003cem\u003eAssassin’s Creed Shadows\u003c/em\u003e features both, and you can even customize your base—otherwise known as your hideout—with cherry blossom trees, deer statues, intricate pathways, and so much more. Unfortunately, it’ll cost you. Who knew interior and exterior decorating would be such a lucrative market in Feudal Japan?! - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-hideout-customization-unlock-1851772163\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-hideout-customization-unlock-1851772163\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"1c9c037afd49eb6488857fc259d4426a\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1c9c037afd49eb6488857fc259d4426a\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An abaonded telephone booth sits in an irradiated wasteland.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An abaonded telephone booth sits in an irradiated wasteland.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/1c9c037afd49eb6488857fc259d4426a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/1c9c037afd49eb6488857fc259d4426a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/1c9c037afd49eb6488857fc259d4426a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An abaonded telephone booth sits in an irradiated wasteland.\" data-chomp-id=\"1c9c037afd49eb6488857fc259d4426a\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"An abaonded telephone booth sits in an irradiated wasteland.\